---
// Component to recreate the "What is Scratch" section exactly like the original
---

<section class="bg-white py-16">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Content Section - Left side with star bullets -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8" style="color: #1e293b;">甚麼是Scratch？</h2>
        
        <!-- Star bullet points - exact match to original -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <!-- Feature 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <i class="far fa-star text-gray-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                由 MIT 開發的一套電腦程序開發平台
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <i class="far fa-star text-gray-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                一個運用編程及繪圖說故事的地方，學生可以透過拖拉積木實現所想。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Feature 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
              <i class="far fa-star text-gray-600 text-xl"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
                一個將想法形象化的地方。學生更可以在社群內互相學習互相分享。
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image Section - Right side with Scratch cat -->
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <img 
          src="/media/Screenshot-2023-09-08-at-8.13.03-PM-min-1024x484.png" 
          alt="Scratch Interface with Cat"
          class="w-full max-w-md h-auto"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Learn Scratch Section - match original with check marks -->
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8" style="color: #1e293b;">為甚麼要學Scratch?</h2>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Check mark items - match original -->
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-gray-600 text-xl"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
              <span class="font-medium">易入手</span> - 只要透過拖拉積木便可以將腦內的想法呈現出來
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <i class="fas fa-check-circle text-gray-600 text-xl"></i>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-base">
              <span class="font-medium">提高自信心</span> - 學生只要擁有一個值得自豪的專屬專案，便會更願意分享製作作品的歷程
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 